    "The accurate prediction matches the ground truth label, while misleading knowledge does not.",
    "Meanwhile, precise knowledge has low entropy, while ambiguity implies high entropy and uncertainty.",
    "The client-side selectors are responsible for filtering out incorrect local predictions, while the server-side selector aims to eliminate ambiguous knowledge.",
